<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="inherit-v">inherit <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'herɪt/    美 /ɪn'herɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>继承 (遗产等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>inherited</strong> a fortune <strong>from</strong> his father.
他从父亲那儿继承了一笔财产。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>经遗传获得 (外貌、性格、特征等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She inherited her mother's curly hair. / She inherited curly hair <strong>from</strong> her mother<strong>inherited_2</strong>
她遗传了她妈妈的卷发。</p></div></div>